---
// FireStats component with enhanced micro-interactions and scroll-triggered animations
---

<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 md:py-16 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-3xl">
        Why Professional Fire Door Inspections Matter
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500 sm:text-lg">
        Most fire doors fail when they're actually checked—often over something
        small and fixable. Regular professional inspection and maintenance is
        what keeps yours working, and keeps you compliant with the Regulatory
        Reform (Fire Safety) Order 2005 and Building Regulations Approved
        Document B.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12">
      <dl
        class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 sm:divide-x sm:divide-gray-100"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col px-4 py-8 text-center stat-card transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <dt class="order-last text-lg font-medium text-gray-500">
            Fire doors fail professional inspection
          </dt>

          <dd class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand">
            75%
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col px-4 py-8 text-center stat-card transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <dt class="order-last text-lg font-medium text-gray-500">
            Communal fire door checks required*
          </dt>

          <dd class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand">
            Quarterly
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col px-4 py-8 text-center stat-card transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <dt class="order-last text-lg font-medium text-gray-500">
            From first call to final report
          </dt>

          <dd class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand">
            Same inspector
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col px-4 py-8 text-center stat-card transition-transform duration-300"
        >
          <dt class="order-last text-lg font-medium text-gray-500">
            Years of joinery &amp; construction experience
          </dt>

          <dd class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand">
            35+
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>

      <p class="mt-6 text-center text-sm text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        75% figure: Fire Door Inspection Scheme, based on 100,000+ inspections
        (2021). *Quarterly checks of communal fire doors apply in residential
        buildings over 11m under the Fire Safety (England) Regulations 2022.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Regulatory Compliance Section -->
    <div class="mt-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">
        Key Fire Safety Regulations
      </h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand mb-2">Building Regulations</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Approved Document B - Fire Safety: Volume 1 (Dwellings) and Volume 2
            (Buildings other than dwellings)
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand mb-2">RRO 2005</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Regulatory Reform (Fire Safety) Order 2005 - Requires regular fire
            risk assessments and maintenance
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand mb-2">British Standards</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            BS 9999:2017 and BS 8214:2016 - Fire safety design and fire door
            assembly standards
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Stat card hover effects */
  .stat-card {
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Disable hover effects on touch devices */
  @media (hover: none) {
    .stat-card:hover {
      transform: none;
      box-shadow: none;
    }
  }
</style>
